node.text:
Winter and mask irritation has been drying and breaking out my face. Here’s how I rebalance my skin throughout these zoom calls. 

Products 
* Face Cuddle Moisture Balm @emcosmetics 
* Lip Cushion Nourishing Balm @emcosmetics
* Midnight Patches @doe.bby 
* Soft Shield Patches @sokoglam

node.title: My WFH Self Care Skin Routine

node.text: So Soft is so so soft ☁️ Look how easy it is to blend. @emcosmetics #emcosmetics #madewithmagic

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ℳ 𓂀 on July 22, 2021 tagging @emcosmetics. May be an image of cosmetics.

node.text:
So Soft ( blush and contour ) is now available! This is my current favorite blush formula. It’s truly soft like a cloud, with a skin-like finish. It packs a lot of pigment, but foolproof because it blends with ease. A lot of love went into these babies. We hope you enjoy it! @emcosmetics 

☁️ Formulated with our Satin Cloud Complex, a unique blend of rich powders and emollients that create a luxurious air-whipped, mousse-like texture. 

🌙 Enriched with Squalane & Vitamin E to help condition skin and provide antioxidant defense. 

💧 Soft, sensorial texture blends and layers seamlessly for customizable color and dimension with a soft satin, skin-like finish. 

Cruelty-free and gluten-free 🐰 
#emcosmetics
